Synopsis: The Addams Family is being targeted by a crazed TV host who tries to run them out of their own neighbourhood. Pugsley has to get ready for the big family reunion and poor Wednesday has to face the biggest horror of all time; high school.  This family’s lives are turned upside down when they realize that the town next door is suddenly full of uptight suburbanites who are led by the very same TV host who will stop at nothing to get rid of the freakish Addams family to build her own perfect world. Starring: Oscar Isaac, Charlize Theron, Chloë Grace Moretz, Finn Wolfhard, Nick Kroll and Snoop Dogg. Directed by: Conrad Vernon and Greg Tiernan      